data.clean_description: Tincture made from CO2 extracted CBD and hemp oil. The CBD is derived from organically grown cannabis and is made under lab conditions. Dosage 1 - 10 drops 3 times per day. The tincture can best be ingested as drops , letting the oil sit below your tongue for about a minute , then swallowing. It can also be used in cooking , tea , coffee or similarly , but be careful with hot products , as it will destroy the CBD. Bottlecap has a dripper attached for easy dosage. Contains 10 ml per bottle. max quantity. 2 per order due to shippingfee s. Choose additional shipping when ordering more than 2 bottles. NOTE Picture is from a 200 mg bottle , the bottle looks the same except the 500 mg mas 500 mg written.
data.name: 10ml CBD(500mg) Tincture Hemp Seed Oil
